title: Install Unity To OpenXR Step By Step (Hello Unity) #NoTalk 2023-03
description:
This video is a step by step guide of how to create a quick project under Unity that is ready in OpenXR to be used for someone that never used Unity.
There are not voice because I plan to do it later on. But in case I don't, I uploaded this video. (This is a part one in long video workshop).
More on the project here:  https://github.com/EloiStree/2023_03_03_HelloNoCodeJamXR
author: Éloi Strée, ꬲ🧰: Raw video
